"Breakout.instructions" = "# Breakout\n\nBounce a ball off your paddle to break every brick.\n\n## How to play\n\n- **Drag** anywhere on the play area to move the paddle left or right.\n- Keep the ball in play — if it falls below the paddle, you lose a life.\n- Hit every brick to clear the level and advance.\n\n## Power-ups\n\nSome bricks drop power-ups when broken. Catch them with the paddle for short-lived bonuses such as a wider paddle, a slower ball, or extra balls.\n\n## Lives and game over\n\nYou start with a few lives. Lose all of them and the game ends. Clearing every brick advances you to the next, faster level.";
